        <abstract>
            <p>Asks for list of families of sleeping plants. Believes sleep is merely modified circumnutation at a particular time of day.</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Porlieria</hi> has had no water for some time but shows no sign of flagging.</p>  
<p>Describes the response of <hi rend="italic">Thalia</hi> flowers to touch.</p> 
        </abstract>
